platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Coloring. It’s fun, creative, and just for little kids. Right? Wrong. Once you get your hands on this virtual coloring book—designed for adults—you’ll wise up to this one simple fact: we never should have quit. Each illustration is wonderful designed, and we loved switching between watercolors, colored pencils, and pens to make every piece unique.
用線條療癒心靈, 以色彩抒解壓力。由畫家用心設計, 包括花草樹木、飛鳥走獸及昆蟲等多款精美細緻的圖畫, 讓你可以無拘無束、自然隨心地塗上繽紛色彩。《Tayasui Color》逼真的填色工具, 模擬真實畫具, 其特色水彩濕畫筆會透過獨特的力度感應來調整顏色深淺。填色時發出的高度仿真聲效, 帶來極為真實的繪畫體驗, 助你紓緩都市壓力。
